name: Sarova Stanley
description: Sarova Stanley is a furnished and modest property located in Regimental Bazaar, Shivaji Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana. The property is in close vicinity to multiple tourist spots namely Sanjeeviah Park, Buddha Statue, Snow World, and Birla Science Museum.

name: Villa Rosa Kempinski
description: Villa Rosa Kempinski is a luxurious hotel located in the heart of the city. Enjoy the comfort and elegance of our deluxe rooms, and explore nearby attractions such as shopping malls and cultural landmarks.

name: Nairobi Serena Hotel
description: Nairobi Serena Hotel is a furnished and modest property located in Regimental Bazaar, Shivaji Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana. The property is in close vicinity to multiple tourist spots namely Sanjeeviah Park, Buddha Statue, Snow World, and Birla Science Museum.

name: Mara Serena Safari Lodge
description: Mara Serena Safari Lodge offers a unique safari experience in the heart of the Maasai Mara. Enjoy the beauty of the African wilderness and comfortable accommodations at our lodge.

name: Fairmont The Norfolk
description: Fairmont The Norfolk is a historic hotel located in the heart of Nairobi. Experience the charm of colonial-era architecture and enjoy a relaxing stay in our non-deluxe rooms.
